<TEXT>
 

2. The first time Mr. Wicks is employed in NRC-licensed activities following the five-year prohibition, he shall
notify the Director, Office of Enforcement, U.S. Nuclear Regulatory Commission, Washington, D.C. 20555 and the
Regional Administrator, NRC Region IV, at least five days prior to the performance of licensed activities (as described
in 1 above). The notice shall include the name, address, and telephone number of the NRC or Agreement State licensee
