The Commission notes that this amendment merely conforms the NASD's rules to those of the NYSE which do not contain
a minimum holder requirement for hybrid debt securities.
 Accordingly, the Commission believes that this amendment does not raise any significant regulatory issues.





For the above reasons, the Commission believes it is consistent with section 15A(b)(6)
