from the Institute and a disclaimer paragraph based on the example provided in section X.Q. of the Guideline. The ``SJI''
logo must appear on the front cover of a written product, or in the opening frames of a video product, unless the Institute
approves another placement. 



Twenty copies of all project products, including videotapes, must be submitted to the Institute. In addition, a copy
