2. Responsibilities of State Supreme Court 


Each application for funding from a State or local court must be approved, consistent with State law, by the State's
Supreme Court, or its designated agency or council. 
The State Supreme Court or its designee shall receive all Institute funds awarded to such courts; shall be responsible
for assuring proper administration of Institute funds; and shall be responsible for all aspects of the project, including
